<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email Address - Booking System</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; 
            color: #333; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            background-color: #ffffff; 
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 14px;
        }
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo img {
            max-width: 150px;
        }
        h1 { 
            color: #b23ff0; 
            margin-top: 0; 
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        p { 
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            font-size: 16px; 
        }
        .button { 
            display: inline-block; 
            padding: 12px 24px; 
            font-size: 16px; 
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            background-color: #b23ff0; 
            color: #fff; 
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .button:hover { 
            background-color: #b23ff0; 
        }
        .footer { 
            margin-top: 40px; 
            padding-top: 20px; 
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; 
            color: #666; 
            font-size: 14px; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Booking System</h1>
        <p>Dear {{firstName}} {{lastName}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing our booking system. We're excited to have you on board! To get started and ensure the security of your account, please verify your email address.</p>
        <p>
            <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
        </p>
        <p>This link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons. If you don't verify within this time, you may need to request a new verification email.</p>

        <p>Once your email is verified, you'll have full access to these features and more. We're committed to making your booking experience as smooth and efficient as possible.</p>

        <p>If you did not register for our service or have any questions, please contact our support team at support@yourbookingsystem.com.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Booking System Team</p>
            <p>Â© 2023 Your Booking System. All rights reserved.<br>
            123 Booking Street, City, Country 12345</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
